    "stage": "初级",
    "chapter": "11.5 项目实训——汽车图片资源下载",
    "chapter_num": 11,
    "knowledge_tag": "爬虫进阶",
    "question_type": "code",
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "question": "代码题：使用requests和Beautiful Soup下载网页中的所有图片。",
    "options": [],
    "answer": "参考代码：\nimport requests\nfrom bs4 import BeautifulSoup\nimport os\nfrom urllib.parse import urljoin\n\ndef download_images(url, save_dir='images'):\n    \"\"\"\n    下载网页中的所有图片\n    \"\"\"\n    # 创建保存目录\n    if not os.path.exists(save_dir):\n        os.makedirs(save_dir)\n    \n    # 请求头\n    headers = {\n        'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36'\n    }\n    \n    try:\n        # 1. 请求网页\n        response = requests.get(url, headers=headers, timeout=10)\n        response.encoding = 'utf-8'\n        print(f'网页请求成功，状态码：{response.status_code}')\n        \n        # 2. 解析HTML，提取所有图片URL\n        soup = BeautifulSoup(response.text, 'html.parser')\n        img_tags = soup.find_all('img')\n        print(f'找到 {len(img_tags)} 张图片')\n        \n        # 3. 下载并保存图片\n        success_count = 0\n        for i, img in enumerate(img_tags, 1):\n            # 获取图片URL\n            img_url = img.get('src') or img.get('data-src')\n            if not img_url:\n                continue\n            \n            # 处理相对路径，转为绝对路径\n            img_url = urljoin(url, img_url)\n            \n            # 获取图片文件名\n            filename = os.path.basename(img_url.split('?')[0])\n            if not filename or '.' not in filename:\n                filename = f'image_{i}.jpg'\n            \n            save_path = os.path.join(save_dir, filename)\n            \n            try:\n                # 下载图片\n                img_response = requests.get(img_url, headers=headers, timeout=10)\n                \n                # 保存图片\n                with open(save_path, 'wb') as f:\n                    f.write(img_response.content)\n                \n                print(f'  [{i}/{len(img_tags)}] 下载成功：{filename}')\n                success_count += 1\n                \n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f'  [{i}/{len(img_tags)}] 下载失败：{filename} - {e}')\n                continue\n        \n        print(f'\\n下载完成！成功 {success_count} 张，失败 {len(img_tags) - success_count} 张')\n        print(f'图片保存在：{os.path.abspath(save_dir)}')\n        \n    except requests.exceptions.RequestException as e:\n        print(f'网页请求失败：{e}')\n\n# 使用示例\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # 示例：下载某个网页的图片\n    url = 'https://www.example.com/cars'  # 替换为实际网址\n    print('开始下载图片...')\n    print(f'目标网页：{url}')\n    print('=' * 50)\n    download_images(url)\n\n预期输出（示意）：\n开始下载图片...\n目标网页：https://www.example.com/cars\n==================================================\n网页请求成功，状态码：200\n找到 12 张图片\n  [1/12] 下载成功：car1.jpg\n  [2/12] 下载成功：car2.jpg\n  [3/12] 下载失败：car3.jpg - 超时\n  ...\n\n下载完成！成功 10 张，失败 2 张\n图片保存在：/path/to/images",
    "analysis": "本题考察图片爬虫的完整实现，综合运用requests请求、Beautiful Soup解析、文件操作、异常处理等知识，是本章的综合实战。",
