    "options": [],
    "answer": "参考代码：\n\ndef parse(self, response):\n    '''\n    解析图书列表页，提取图书信息和详情页链接\n    '''\n    # 获取列表中的所有图书\n    books = response.xpath('//ul[@class=\"bigimg\"]/li')\n    \n    for book in books:\n        item = DangdangBookItem()\n        \n        # 提取书名\n        item['title'] = book.xpath('.//a/@title').get()\n        \n        # 提取价格\n        item['price'] = book.xpath('.//span[@class=\"search_now_price\"]/text()').get()\n        \n        # 提取作者\n        item['author'] = book.xpath('.//p[@class=\"search_book_author\"]/span[1]/a/@title').get()\n        \n        # 提取出版社\n        item['publisher'] = book.xpath('.//p[@class=\"search_book_author\"]/span[3]/a/@title').get()\n        \n        # 提取详情页URL\n        detail_url = book.xpath('.//a/@href').get()\n        item['detail_url'] = detail_url\n        \n        # 方式一：直接返回列表页提取的信息\n        # yield item\n        \n        # 方式二：构造详情页请求，获取更完整的信息\n        if detail_url:\n            yield scrapy.Request(\n                url=detail_url,\n                callback=self.parse_detail,\n                meta={'item': item}\n            )\n    \n    # 翻页：提取下一页链接\n    next_page = response.xpath('//a[@class=\"next\"]/@href').get()\n    if next_page:\n        yield scrapy.Request(url=next_page, callback=self.parse)\n\ndef parse_detail(self, response):\n    '''\n    解析图书详情页，获取更完整的信息\n    '''\n    item = response.meta['item']\n    \n    # 提取ISBN\n    item['isbn'] = response.xpath('//span[contains(text(), \"ISBN\")]/following-sibling::text()').get()\n    \n    # 添加爬取时间\n    from datetime import datetime\n    item['crawl_time'] = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\n    \n    yield item\n\n代码说明：\n- parse方法解析列表页，提取基本信息并构造详情页请求\n- 使用meta传递item到详情页解析函数\n- parse_detail方法解析详情页，补充ISBN等更详细的信息\n- 实现了翻页功能，可以自动爬取多页",
